	* plug-ins/metadata/xmp-parse.c: protect against broken XMP blocks
	using rdf:Alt instead of rdf:Seq.  Fixes bug #343315.

	* plug-ins/metadata/xmpdump.c (main): call g_set_prgname() to get
	better messages from glib.

