2006-05-16  Michael Natterer  <mitch@gimp.org>

	* app/core/Makefile.am
	* app/core/core-types.h
	* app/core/gimppatternclipboard.[ch]: new GimpPattern subclass
	that auto-updates its contents from gimp->global_buffer.

