2005-09-26  Michael Natterer  <mitch@gimp.org>

	Allow to disable the color picker info dialog. Fixes bug #315011:

	* app/tools/tools-enums.[ch] (enum GimpColorPickerMode): added
	value GIMP_COLOR_PICK_MODE_PALETTE.

