	some mem-leaks reported by valgrind.

2005-01-14  Jay Cox  <jaycox@gimp.org>

	* plug-ins/common/psd_save.c: Much less wasted memory.  Save guides.
	Fixes bug #151904.

2005-01-14  Michael Natterer  <mitch@gimp.org>

